      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear that, but for a small business owner in my district, \"long-term necessity\" doesn't pay the bills next month. it feels like the regs are written for huge corporations and just leave the little guys to struggle. do u think there's any real weight to the argument that these policies might actually be harming the economic stability of these local communities?",
